{
  "stem": "6195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I wouldn't let my father out by himself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Wherever he had to go, I went with him to sort of protect him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But how I could protect him, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just had the feeling I didn't want him to be alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we lived like this with every day, new, new things, new rules coming up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not to employ non-Jewish labor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the maid, of course, had, has gone three days after the war came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Non-Jewish doctors were not to attend to Jewish patients.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Although I must say, when my mother wasn't feeling well, I did manage to get a non-Jewish doctor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came in the dark-- before the curfew, but in the dark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And he, he, he just couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did cut out a lump under her armpit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to take off the Star of David-- because that came into law immediately-- and went to the Institute of Pathology.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And, well, it was cancer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we lived like this till we were taken to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were given 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] No.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I, I jumped something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] something came out that we all have to register.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And people above 50 or whatever-- I can't remember now-- had to leave Cracow [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and go within the perimeter of 30 kilometers, past the perimeter of 30 kilometers from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So obviously, it was my prime interest to set up my father somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
